    • atlas

      public BufferedImage atlas
      Stores the sprites of all tiles in the form of subimages encompassing the larger image atlas.

    • tiles

      public ArrayList<Tile> tiles
      Stores an array list of Tile objects used for rendering a level.
      Each tile is assigned to a smaller array list which is then appended to this main collection.

    • tilesGrassVariants

      public ArrayList<Tile> tilesGrassVariants
      A sub-array list containing GRASS_BASE variants composed of GRASS_VAR_A, GRASS_EDGE_B, and GRASS_VAR_C.

    • tilesGrassEdges

      public ArrayList<Tile> tilesGrassEdges

    • tilesGrassCorners

      public ArrayList<Tile> tilesGrassCorners

    • getSpriteAnimated

      public BufferedImage getSpriteAnimated​(int id, int frame)
      Returns the frame of an animated tile with the passed grid coordinates. Used when first initializing a new animated Tile.
      Parameters:
      id - - The unique identifier of the tile.
      frame - - The current frame of the animated tile.
      Returns:
      image - The image of the tile with the passed id in the defined frame.
